{"tid":1831647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國聾人起訴 Pornhub 沒有提供字幕   稱影響其享受影片內容","createTime":"2020-01-20T14:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T16:17:56.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bb7d0e89806bb04eae5ad047a7164fe8da04fb","tid":1831647,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96-6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F%25E6%2593%25B7%25E5%258F%2596-6.png&h=ef8792ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著全球現時正追求不同人士之間的平等對待，就連網上亦應該有相同的想法。近日，美國就有一名聾人在瀏覽成人網站 Pornhub 時，發現部分影片並沒有提供字幕，而致其無法享受影片中的內容，決定就著有關問題以「構成歧視」為由起訴 Pornhub。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/PornHub-NYC-store-1280x854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FPornHub-NYC-store-1280x854.jpg&h=ba56fbbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自美國紐約的 Yaroslav Suris 指自己在今個月瀏覽 Pornhub 時，發現並非所有的影片亦有提供字幕，從而使到其無法享受影片中的劇情以及內容，認為網站對一眾聾人以及聽力有問題的人士構成了歧視，在日前正式起訴 Pornhub，希望對方進行賠償。<br />\n<br />\n在事件被曝光後網民紛紛指有關的起訴事件極為罕有，更在網上流傳後使到 Pornhub 的副總裁親自回應，他指網站內其實有一個專門的字幕類別，並沒有特意針對部分傷殘人士。美國其實在 1990 年曾推出一項《殘疾人法案》，但當中就沒有特別指明成人影片是否應納入保障的範圍之一，只是說明傷殘人士應與普通人具有相同的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/20/pornhub-sued-by-deaf-man-over-lack-of-captions/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F20%2Fpornhub-sued-by-deaf-man-over-lack-of-captions%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9y6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=de990d53\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/20/pornhub-sued-by-deaf-man-over-lack-of-captions/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"af0fc7b1767754762e3abc10df433bf3eb850acf","tid":1831647,"uid":34714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"fuck me fuck me o